1. Elektron pochta xabarining umumiy koâ€˜rinishi

Mavzu (Subject): URGENT: Your Account Will Be Suspended!

Joâ€˜natuvchi (From): support@paypal-security.com

Xodimga koâ€˜ringan manzil: support@paypal.com

Xabar tarkibi:

