2. Elektron pochta headerlarini tahlil qilish

Elektron pochtaning texnik tafsilotlarini tekshiramiz:

Return-Path: <hacker@malicious.com>
Received: from mail-malicious.com ([198.51.100.25])
    by mail.company.com with SMTP;
X-Mailer: Microsoft Outlook Express 6.00.2900.5512
Subject: URGENT: Your Account Will Be Suspended!
From: "PayPal Support" <support@paypal-security.com>
Reply-To: <hacker@malicious.com>

ğŸ“Œ Zaiflik va shubhali belgilar:

âœ… "From" manzili: support@paypal-security.com, lekin asl PayPal manzili emas (oâ€˜zini PayPal deb koâ€˜rsatgan).
âœ… "Return-Path" va "Reply-To": Ular hacker@malicious.com domeniga ishora qilmoqda.
âœ… "Received from" qatorida: Elektron pochta 198.51.100.25 IP manzilidan kelgan, bu ruxsatsiz server boâ€˜lishi mumkin.

âœ… Domenni tekshiramiz:

whois paypal-security.com
dig paypal-security.com

Natijada, domen yaqinda roâ€˜yxatdan oâ€˜tgan yoki PayPalâ€™ga aloqador emas ekanligi aniqlanadi.


